revisions.description: Changes are done to change all Data packet/octet counters from 32 to 64 bit counter. 32 bit counters were too small for data packets/octects and were consumed too early. All old counters are deprecated and new counters are added.
Updated the revision history and LAST-UPDATED field.
Changed the data type of jnxL2tpSessionStatsInterfaceUnit from Integer32 to Unsigned32.
